SEDUCTION: Using charm and attraction to manipulate

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 22% (+3%/level, cap 98%)

Using physical charm, flattery, and attraction to win someone's trust,
extract information, or talk your way into something you shouldn't
have access to. A favorite of spies, con artists, and rogues who
would rather charm their way past a problem than fight through it.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, streetwise, disguise
